
we organize automation project files/folders in structured or organized manner.

objective
==========
1 reusability
2 maintainability
3 readability

bulid-in -framework
        ex - testng , junit , cucumber Bdd , robot etc

customized (user defined) -framework
            modular frame , data driven , keyword driven , hybrid driven etc

phase
======

1 . Analysing Aut (understand the application)
        - Number of pages
        - What are all elements / how / type
        - what to automate & what not to be automate

2 . choose Test case for automation

        1 . 10 Test case  ----- 90 automatable  10 cannot automatable  ( 100% possible in these context )
        2 . sanity/smoke - p1
        3 . data driven test  - p2
        4 . regression -p2
        5 . any other cases - p4

3 Design & Development of framework

4 Execution - local [ide] , remotely [git] , jenkin

5 Maintenance

